=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Overviews_Operators_ex10 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 501 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and sustained envelope, energy distribution is late, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: sustained
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: late

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 501.0658
  harmonic_decay_rate: -8.1888
  harmonic_regularity: 0.1784
  pitch_clarity: 92.0818
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -5.4352
  resonance_freq: 495.2637

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Operators Example 10
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Overviews/Operators.html
// Tags: Operators, Overviews
// ---
// --- Example 10 ---
(
{
    var a;
    a = Line.ar(-2, 2, 0.01);
    a.softclip
}.plot
)


{ FSinOsc.ar(500,0.0, XLine.kr(0.1, 10, 10)).softclip * 0.25 }.play;
